review: Dr Jayaram is an excellent doctor.he spends lot of time listening to parents concerns.he is very caring and friendly towards children.most importantly he does not prescribe medicine /tests unless required.i would definitely recommend him
Awesome human being who listens to the patient carefully and gives treatment. Prescribes less medication and good guidance.

review: Doctor support is good. ** ***** *********** ********* Following up visit for patient is good. He is friendly doctor. Treats child with care.
Doctor is not coming to this clinic now the doctor is visiting some other hospital but the clinic receptionist don't know which hospital so check
Doctor gave proper attention to the baby. And talked to us, patently answered all our queries. We were satisfied talking to him.
The investigation was done systematically and the medication prescribed was helpful in curing the fever.Need more such doctors
